node.title: This week on "Face the Nation with Margaret Brennan," February 13, 2022
node.description: White House national security adviser Jake Sullivan, New Jersey Governor Phil Murphy and more appear on "Face the Nation with Margaret Brennan" on Sunday.
node.content: ["Jake Sullivan - White House national security adviser", "Governor Phil Murphy - (R) New Jersey\u00a0", "Representative Adam Kinzinger - (R) Illinois\u00a0", "Dr. Scott Gottlieb - Former FDA Commissioner, Pfizer board member", "Mary Daly - President and CEO, Federal Reserve Bank of San Francisco", "James Brown - CBS News special correspondent, host of \"The NFL Today\"", "Date: Sunday, February 13, 2022", "TV: \"Face the Nation\" airs Sunday mornings on CBS.
